text: Miss Thailand World 2016 was the 27th edition of the Miss Thailand World auditioned on April 21-April 24, 2016.รับสมัคร มิสไทยแลนด์เวิลด์ 2016 โค้งสุดท้าย พยาบาล-นศ.ร่วมประชันโฉม Pageant held at Grand Hyatt Erawan Hotel in BangkokMTW 2016 รอบ 30 คนสุดท้าย on 28 May 2016. Thunyachanok Moonnilta from Chiang Mai crowned her successor at the end of the event. The coronation pageant was broadcast live on Channel 3 Thailand. The crowned winner was Jinnita Buddee of Chiang Rai, who later represented Thailand at the Miss World 2016 competition in the Washington, D.C., United States and finished in the top 20. == Final results == {| class="wikitable" style="font-size: 95%;" |- !Final Results !Contestant |- | Miss Thailand World 2016 | *' - Jinnita Buddee |- | 1st Runner-Up | *' - Patlada Kulphakthanapat |- | 2nd Runner-Up | *' - Natthakamol Suwansilp |- | Top 5 | *' - Chanya Wonglappanich *' - Sudaporn Wongsasiriphat |- | Top 10 | *' - Leenar Divis *' - Sunisa Ketkaew *' - Juthamanee Parasingha *' - Phijittra Kongson *'' - Malinee Boon-on |} == Special Award== {| class="wikitable" style="font-size: 95%;" |- !
